{"tid":563880,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"『集思廣益』如何合符經濟效益地剃鬚","createTime":"2018-02-17T11:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T11:39:20.000Z","uid":169530,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"27c5ed290c022499b3eb7691eb4285b426ea42da","tid":563880,"uid":169530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T11:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/17/191120_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F17%2F191120_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=eaf0c8ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信各位巴打每隔幾日 甚至每日都會係廁所入面做一件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係剃鬚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你諗下 一把菜刀咁大塊不鏽鋼都係賣緊53蚊一把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解剃鬚刀片要賣到18x蚊4塊咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時係到諗寧願用菜刀剃算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 剃到鈍左又可以磨返利佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 合符經濟效益之餘仲可以保護環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d1063bef7f33a6f9feffd24e7c8a06802e4dac","tid":563880,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T11:19:31.000Z","msg":"用二個五毫子夾最平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537326dd7b909518e8c01acdee34cfd8c191876d","tid":563880,"uid":169530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14d1063bef7f33a6f9feffd24e7c8a06802e4dac","tid":563880,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-